# Prototype Builder

## Purpose
Scaffold UI flows quickly using mock data or API simulators.

## Workflow
1. Generate page or component using current design patterns.
2. Create mock API handlers using MSW or Faker.js.
3. Simulate realistic UX flows (loading, success, error).
4. Annotate mocks for easy replacement with real APIs.
